== Locos x Rails I18n Demonstration

This is a very simple, bare-bone Rails 2.3.2 demonstration
app whose purpose is to show up the I18n APIs and the
several different ways to deal with I18n.

It also shows up a few important plugins/gems such as

* Sven's routing-filter
* Fast Backend version of I18n
* Joshua's Globalize2

Author: http://www.akitaonrails.com